name: Prince Consort
description: The ever present companion to the Faerie Queen. A jokester. A dandy. But do not mistakes his quick wit for generosity. The Prince Consort is a consummate opportunist, second only in shrewd conniving to the Queen herself. He will greet you with a grand banquet. If you eat you will be forever in his thrall. If you refuse, you will gravely insult his magnificence. Oh the troubles we've seen...
